    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "Good, trained staff and HOD also students. Three to four exams will be conducted.",
        "Many automation internships are conducted by different companies, based on PLC, LabVIEW, and MATLAB.",
        "With regards to my internship, the head of my department, Prof. M. KUMARAN, used to suggest the best organization to work in order to gain knowledge.",
        "If you are going to have a loan from the bank, they accept many types of government banks.",
        "There are many books in the library, and the class environment is excellent. Additionally, there are numerous extracurricular activities.",
        "Also, they provide cart tables, chairs, and weekly room cleaning services. Additionally, there are cleaning staff available, but they will ask for money if you want tea.",
        "Our college has an amazing infrastructure that they have been expanding over the years. This allows them to provide better facilities for both students and faculty."
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        "Learning the stuff they taught you in books is inadequate for getting placed in companies.",
        "The gifts were toothpicks and pen stands, as if we were so poor that we couldnt afford toothpicks and lacked oral hygiene, so they thought.",
        "The campus was horrible in that way, and no support was given by the department, even in job searching or assisting students to find a job.",
        "Male students were made to bathe on the open terrace due to inadequate water. The food quality was poor, and there were four students in each room. There was a lack of electricity for half the time, and the use of phones and laptops was not allowed"
      ]
